.sheet-Luck-Specials
	.sheet-Subsection
		input.sheet-SettingCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_Game-World', value='0')
		span(data-i18n='luck').sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches Luck
		span.sheet-Setting-Bone
			+translate('Favour')
		|  
		span(data-i18n='special') Special
	input.sheet-checkbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-LuckSpecial', value='1', checked='')
	span.sheet-anglebox
	span.sheet-ExpHeader
	.sheet-Expander
		input.sheet-SettingCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_Game-World', value='0')
		input.sheet-SkinCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_SkinCheck', value='0')
		.sheet-Setting-Bone
			input.sheet-SkinCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_SkinCheck', value='0')
			.sheet-Chosen
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, the Keeper will bring your fate into play.')
			.sheet-Initiate
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, something goes wrong for your Sect: an ill-advised project or a disastrous operation.')
			.sheet-Crooked
				// Loner
				+translate('Whenever you spend a <i>Favour</i> point, one of your enemies appears to get in your way or a favour you owe comes due.')
			.sheet-Expert
				// Lore-Holder
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, you discover something happening now is related to something you were involved in years ago.')
			.sheet-Mundane
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, you’ll find something weird—maybe even useful!')
			.sheet-Monstrous
				// Other-Folk
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, your monster side gains power: your Curse may become stronger, or another Breed disadvantage may manifest.')
			.sheet-Pararomantic
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, also mark off one of your relationship status boxes. The Keeper will bring <i>fate of your love</i> into play.')
			.sheet-Divine
				// Spirit-Touched
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, either your patron spirit has an urgent and dangerous job for you, or one of its enemies comes after you.')
			.sheet-Spooky
				+translate('As you mark off <i>Favour</i> boxes, your dark side’s needs will get nastier.')
			.sheet-Wronged
				+translate('When you spend a point of <i>Favour</i>, you find a dangerous lead on your prey.')
		.sheet-Setting-Default.sheet-Setting-Gothic.sheet-Setting-Dreaming.sheet-Setting-Marches
			input.sheet-SkinCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_SkinCheck', value='0')
			.sheet-Chosen
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-chosen')
					| When you spend 
					i Luck
					| , the Keeper will bring your fate into play.
			.sheet-Crooked
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-Crooked')
					| When you spend 
					i Luck
					| , someone from your past will re-appear in your life. Soon.
			.sheet-Divine
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-divine')
					| When you spend 
					i Luck
					| , you get word that your Mission requires something difficult that must be done. By you. Urgently.
			.sheet-Expert
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-expert')
			.sheet-Initiate
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-initiate')
			.sheet-Monstrous
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-monstrous')
			.sheet-Mundane
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-mundane')
			.sheet-Spooky
				span.sheet-highlights(data-i18n='luck-special-spooky')
